OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781187095
OL,3,CUniversity of Nottingham student and
OL,4,Calumni data leaked after cyber hack
OL,6,FHackers from a well known
OL,7,Fcybercriminal group have accessed
OL,8,Fpersonal student data held by the
OL,9,FUniversity of Nottingham.
OL,11,FThe Russell Group university said on
OL,12,FWednesday that a "significant" amount
OL,13,Fof data from its student record system
OL,14,Fwas breached, possibly including
OL,15,Ffinancial information.
OL,17,FIt is understood the university
OL,18,Fidentified the unauthorised activity
OL,19,Fon its campus solutions system on
OL,20,FTuesday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
