FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781187095
OL,3,CUniversity of Nottingham student and
OL,4,Calumni data leaked after cyber hack
OL,6,FThe University of Nottingham say that
OL,7,Fstudent and alumni data has been
OL,8,Fcompromised.
OL,10,FThey also say they have established a
OL,11,Fdedicated support line for those
OL,12,Fimpacted.
OL,14,FA university spokesperson said: "The
OL,15,FUniversity of Nottingham has been the
OL,16,Fvictim of a cyber incident and a
OL,17,Fsignificant amount of data in our
OL,18,Fstudent record system has been
OL,19,Faccessed by a well-known cybercriminal
OL,20,Fgroup.
OL,26,@vD@aOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781187095
OL,3,CUniversity of Nottingham student and
OL,4,Calumni data leaked after cyber hack
OL,6,F"We are working with the third party
OL,7,Fthat maintains the platform to lead a
OL,8,Fforensic investigation.
OL,10,F"We understand that those affected
OL,11,Fwill have concerns about what this
OL,12,Fmeans for their personal data and we
OL,13,Fwill be offering advice and support to
OL,14,Four students as we learn more.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781187095
OL,3,CUniversity of Nottingham student and
OL,4,Calumni data leaked after cyber hack
OL,6,F"We take the privacy and security of
OL,7,Fdata that we hold seriously, and we
OL,8,Fhave reported this incident to Action
OL,9,FFraud and the Information
OL,10,FCommissioner's Office. The university
OL,11,Fwill continue to provide them with
OL,12,Ffurther information as our
OL,13,Finvestigation progresses."
OL,15,FThe university said in an email to
OL,16,Fstudents that contact information,
OL,17,Fcourse information and financial
OL,18,Finformation may have been accessed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
