PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781187095
OL,3,CUniversity of Nottingham student and
OL,4,Calumni data leaked after cyber hack
OL,6,FThe university urged people to monitor
OL,7,Ftheir accounts for anything suspicious
OL,8,Fand update any passwords for accounts
OL,9,Fthat share credentials with the
OL,10,Funiversity systems.
OL,12,FIt apologised "sincerely" for any
OL,13,Fanxiety caused by the situation and
OL,14,Fsaid it immediately took affected
OL,15,Fsystems offline before launching an
OL,16,Finvestigation.
